snippet: After losses a day earlier, the stock market moved higher, with deal reports and solid earnings from General Motors buoying investors.
abstract: Stocks rise, led by gains at energy and health care companies, even as crude oil slides again; Down Jones industrial average reaches yet another nominal new high.
lead_paragraph: After losses a day earlier, the stock market moved higher, with deal reports and solid earnings from General Motors buoying investors.

headline.main: Dow Industrials Climb Higher on News of Strong Sales at G.M.
